							 Particle-In-Cell (PIC) plasma simulation code

																Patrick Guio

																 June 2000



Introduction
============

This is PicSim, an electrostatic 2.5D (2R3V) and 3D PIC simulation code
suite for magnetised and unmagnetised plasma.

PIC codes come in three different flavours:
1. Boltzmann electrons and particle ions (hybrid) for ion time scale
2. Fixed ions and particle electrons (hybrid) for electron time scale
3. All species as particle


License
=======

PicSim is distributed under the terms of the GNU General Public License.


Content
=======

The mudfas directory contains the multigrid nonlinear Poisson solver with
versatile boundary conditions.

The doc directory contains some documentation about the implementation of
PicSim.


